 ROADS LIE TOGETHER DOCTOR ! HE WANTS ME TO STAND READY TO OBEY ANY SUMMONS THE POLICE MAY SEND ME ! HE HAD BEEN A PRISONER HIMSELF ! BEFORE THE TWO CLERGYMEN HAD GOT HALF WAY DOWN THE STEEP PATH THAT LED FROM THE COMMANDANT'S HOUSE TO THE FLAT ON WHICH THE COTTAGES OF THE DOCTOR AND CHAPLAIN WERE BUILT MACKLEWAIN REJOINED THEM ! HIS OWN SKIN HAD SIZZLED UNDER THE RED HOT BRAND HE MURMURED SOFTLY ! ANOTHER FLOGGING TO MORROW SAID HE GRUMBLINGLY ! YOU DON'T UNDERSTAND HE BEGAN DISDAINFULLY BUT STOPPED SHORT INTIMIDATED BY THE DEAD BLACKNESS OF THE CAVERNOUS EYES IN THE FACE TURNED SLOWLY TOWARDS HIM WITH A BLIND STARE AS IF GUIDED ONLY BY THE SOUND ! WHOM IS HE GOING TO FLOG NOW ! I EMPHASISED COMPLACENTLY ! HE GAVE THE DISCUSSION UP WITH A SLIGHT SHRUG OF THE SHOULDERS ! HE APPEARED TO KNOW FOR HE TOLD ME AT ONCE THAT HE WAS DETECTIVE GRYCE A MAN WHO HAD GROWN OLD IN SOLVING JUST SUCH BAFFLING PROBLEMS AS THESE ! YOU DON'T MEAN TO SAY HE'S GOING TO FLOG KIRKLAND ! HE GAVE UP WORK SOME TIME AGO I HAVE BEEN TOLD MY HUSBAND WENT ON BUT EVIDENTLY A GREAT CASE STILL HAS ITS ALLUREMENT FOR HIM ! PERHAPS YOU'LL HAVE THE GOODNESS TO ALLOW ME TO BE THE BEST JUDGE OF THAT RETURNED MACKLEWAIN DRAWING UP HIS LITTLE BODY TO ITS LEAST INSIGNIFICANT STATURE ! STEVIE ACCUSTOMED TO MOVE ABOUT DISREGARDED HAD GOT UP FROM THE KITCHEN TABLE CARRYING OFF HIS DRAWING TO BED WITH HIM ! MISTER MEEKIN EXPRESSED SOME ALARM BUT DOCTOR MACKLEWAIN RE ASSURED HIM ! THE SHEET OF PAPER COVERED WITH CIRCLES DROPPED OUT OF HIS FINGERS AND HE REMAINED STARING AT THE OLD TERRORIST AS IF ROOTED SUDDENLY TO THE SPOT BY HIS MORBID HORROR AND DREAD OF PHYSICAL PAIN ! THE TRAIL HERE MUST BE A VERY BLIND ONE FOR THEM TO CALL HIM IN ! HIS SCARED EYES BLAZED WITH INDIGNATION IT WOULD HURT TERRIBLY HIS MOUTH DROPPED OPEN ! WE CAN'T DO ANYTHING WITHOUT EVIDENCE COMPLAIN ! I WISH WE HAD NOT LEFT SO SOON ! I SHALL FIND MY PORTMANTEAU IN MY ROOM YOU SAID YES YES ! COMRADE OSSIPON'S FACE TWITCHED WITH EXASPERATION 