 CAME WHISTLING FROM HIS FARM WORK TO LOOK OVER HIS PRETTY CHARGES ! SHALL I POUR OUT MY SOUL INTO THE EAR OF A MIST A FUME FROM MY OWN BRAIN ! WHEN THICKENED STRAIN AND COOL ! THUS WAS SHE BORNE AWAY CAPTIVE OF HER DEAD NEITHER WILLING NOR UNWILLING OF LIFE AND DEATH EQUALLY CARELESS ! BUT FOR THE SIGHT THAT AWAITED HIM HE WAS NOT PREPARED AT ALL ! WITH THAT CAME A PANG OF INTENSE PAIN ! WEEDS MEANWHILE SPRANG UP AND A DREARY CONFUSION REIGNED IN THE ONCE ORDERLY AND BRILLIANT LITTLE GARDEN !
